{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bcc57b96ab","title":"东明作战暂勿举行","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"93f720f417","index":0,"year":1946,"month":5,"day":21,"articleId":"bcc57b96ab"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"838ab2495a","type":"paragraph","text":"东明作战暂勿举行口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"bcc57b96ab"},{"id":"c86bb862ed","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年5月21日）刘、邓：四平已失，为不给顽方以发动大战之借口，东明作战暂勿举行，但对东明、长量、考城、永年、聊城等处进行侦察准备","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"bcc57b96ab"},{"id":"b89b59bcaa","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"bcc57b96ab"},{"id":"cc0f771f8b","type":"paragraph","text":"马卵[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的给香宾鲁豫军区司令员刘伯承和政消委员邓小平的电报。1946年5月20日层刘伯承、邓小平致电中共中央，钱出集中第七级队主力攻取东明，然后再向长短方向发展。同日，毛泽东在是中共中央起草的复电中说：“同意攻取东明，得手后再考成夺取长短，以为感夺税安次、盖县、夏邑、定进四城及向永东区进攻之报复手段。“并询问发意永年、聊城的可能条件。马卵电对原定攻取东明等地的部暑作了修改。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"bcc57b96ab"}],"page":{"id":"513c3119a5","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"bcc57b96ab","start":340,"end":340}}}},"__N_SSG":true}